  "page": "Blood and Cheese",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Blood_the_butcher.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/07/Blood_the_butcher.jpg/350px-Blood_the_butcher.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"420\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/0/07/Blood_the_butcher.jpg 1.5x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Blood_the_butcher.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Blood and Cheese, art by Will Owen</div></div></div>\n<p><b>Blood and Cheese</b> are two individuals who lived during the <a href=\"/index.php/Dance_of_the_Dragons\" title=\"Dance of the Dragons\">Dance of the Dragons</a>. Their real names are not known.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Blood_and_Cheese&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Blood_(butcher)\" title=\"Blood (butcher)\">Blood</a> was a butcher. He was once a <a href=\"/index.php/Serjeant\" title=\"Serjeant\">serjeant</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/City_Watch_of_King%27s_Landing\" title=\"City Watch of King&#39;s Landing\">City Watch of King's Landing</a> and lost his gold cloak for beating a <a href=\"/index.php/Whore\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Whore\">whore</a> to death whilst in a drunken rage. <a href=\"/index.php/Cheese_(ratcatcher)\" title=\"Cheese (ratcatcher)\">Cheese</a> was a ratcatcher familiar with the hidden tunnels of the <a href=\"/index.php/Red_Keep\" title=\"Red Keep\">Red Keep</a>. Together they slew six-year-old Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Jaehaerys_Targaryen_(son_of_Aegon_II)\" title=\"Jaehaerys Targaryen (son of Aegon II)\">Jaehaerys</a>, King <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_II_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon II Targaryen\">Aegon II Targaryen</a>'s firstborn son and the heir to the <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Throne\" title=\"Iron Throne\">Iron Throne</a>, during the Dance of the Dragons.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_a_son_for_a_son.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_a_son_for_a_son.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Blood_and_Cheese&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_a_son_for_a_son.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_a_son_for_a_son.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, The Dying of the Dragons - A Son for a Son.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403165555\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.011 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.012 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 119/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8538/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 454/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 219/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 695/5000000 bytes\n-->\n